        "timestamp": "2018-01-22 22:40:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nFrom Alexei:\n\nIt looks like Git can track rename, but when rename is combined with modify – we get add/delete instead.\n\n[this] has only ecomp -> onap changes, done by commands similar to:\n \nfor i in `find -name logback-test.xml`\ndo\n  j=`basename $i`\n  #echo $i $j\n  sed \"s/org.openecomp.dcae.apod.analytics/org.onap.dcae.apod.analytics/\" $i > /tmp/$j\n  mv /tmp/$j $i\ndone\n \nfor i in `find -name openecomp -type d`\ndo\n  j=`dirname $i`\n  git mv $i $j/onap\ndone\n \nand a few manual edits.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
